display_long_description:
FYYTE is a next-generation VR boxing workout that combines cardio, fun, and real competition. 
Step into the ring and train with legendary MMA champion Jérôme Le Banner. Whether you're looking to work out, train your boxing techniques, or challenge opponents, FYYTE offers you a powerful immersive experience.

Train hard, fight smart – Experience cardio-intense workouts and dynamic fights against your friends or other VR fighters.

Master real boxing moves – Learn punches and how to dodge with voice coaching from Jérôme Le Banner himself.

Game modes – Practice solo or fight in multiplayer.

Immersive environments – Step into a beautifully designed boxing room and arena and feel the thrill of a real fight night.

Whether you're a fitness enthusiast, boxing fan, or VR gamer, FYYTE turns every workout into a knockout.
